Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Holy War=Killing the Inward Dragon
  - 94
---
How long, O man, will thy heart yet slumber? When wilt thou wake from
thy sleep? The world's battles leaving, strengthen thyself, and fight
with thy desire the goodly fight.
